Class CastJiraConnectorBuilder.DescriptorImpl

  • java.lang.Object

    hudson.model.Saveable
    Enclosing class:
    CastJiraConnectorBuilder

    @Extension
public static final class CastJiraConnectorBuilder.DescriptorImpl
extends hudson.tasks.BuildStepDescriptor<hudson.tasks.Builder>
    Descriptor for CastJiraConnectorPlugin. Used as a singleton. The class is marked as public so that it can be accessed from views.

    See src/main/resources/hudson/plugins/hello_world/HelloWorldBuilder/*.jelly for the actual HTML fragment for the configuration screen.
